name: 45 lissajous elves (collector’s single edition)
description: a single image with 45 outputs of a generative system i’ve built in march 2020, initiated from a lissajous curve generator. i tweaked it so much to a certain aesthetic that it ended up in those noisy copies of etheric creatures. inspired by sol lewitt’s ‘incomplete open cubes’, this is a work that celebrates the fruitful recursiveness of generative art.  to the first collector of this single edition, i will send a signed high quality art print of 70x125 cm. please drop me a message on twitter.
